headline_main: California Today: Talking to a Tony Winner

abstract: Philip D. Murphy, now the Democratic nominee for governor, has had the support of national political figures, including former Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr., who stumped for him.
snippet: Philip D. Murphy, now the Democratic nominee for governor, has had the support of national political figures, including former Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr., who stumped for him.
lead_paragraph: UNION CITY, N.J. — The door cracked open slightly, about as far as the chain lock allowed, and Philip D. Murphy hunched over to peer inside.

abstract: The hybrid model gets two more miles to the gallon than the Toyota Prius, and it looks and drives more like a regular gas-powered car.
snippet: The hybrid model gets two more miles to the gallon than the Toyota Prius, and it looks and drives more like a regular gas-powered car.
lead_paragraph: It is the most efficient gasoline-powered car you can buy in America. There’s generous room for four, five if need be. It’s quiet, comfortable and comes with a lifetime battery warranty. And it is not the Toyota Prius.

abstract: The vote by lawmakers was a remarkable rejection of the state’s tax-cutting approach after years of mounting uncertainty and unhappiness over whether it was working.
snippet: The vote by lawmakers was a remarkable rejection of the state’s tax-cutting approach after years of mounting uncertainty and unhappiness over whether it was working.
lead_paragraph: Gov. Sam Brownback’s leadership of Kansas came to be synonymous with a single, unyielding philosophy: Cut taxes, cut the size of government, and the state will thrive.

abstract: Why do America’s black gay and bisexual men have a higher H.I.V. rate than any country in the world?
snippet: Why do America’s black gay and bisexual men have a higher H.I.V. rate than any country in the world?
lead_paragraph: Early on a balmy morning last October, Cedric Sturdevant began his rounds along the bumpy streets and back roads of Jackson, Miss. Sturdevant, 52, has racked up nearly 300,000 miles driving in loops and widening circles around Jackson in his improvised role of visiting nurse, motivational coach and father figure to a growing number of young gay men and transgender women suffering from H.I.V. and AIDS. Sturdevant is a project coordinator at My Brother’s Keeper, a local social-services nonprofit. If he doesn’t make these rounds, he has learned, many of these patients will not get to the doctor’s appointments, pharmacies, food banks and counseling sessions that can make the difference between life and death.

abstract: The party’s fast journey from debating how to combat climate change to arguing against its existence is a story of big political money and Democratic hubris.
snippet: The party’s fast journey from debating how to combat climate change to arguing against its existence is a story of big political money and Democratic hubris.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The campaign ad appeared during the presidential contest of 2008. Rapid-fire images of belching smokestacks and melting ice sheets were followed by a soothing narrator who praised a candidate who had stood up to President George W. Bush and “sounded the alarm on global warming.”

abstract: The luxury sedan arrives looking toned, confident and familiar in a Bentley Flying Spur kind of way. The rest of the car has its own character.
snippet: The luxury sedan arrives looking toned, confident and familiar in a Bentley Flying Spur kind of way. The rest of the car has its own character.
lead_paragraph: The Continental name carries gravitas. So much, in fact, that it’s easy to forget that Lincoln hasn’t used the nameplate since 2002. It’s like realizing that Team Flakes hasn’t been available in the grocery store for years.
headline_main: Video Review: After 15-Year Break, Lincoln Continental Returns With Style
headline_print_headline: Yesteryear’s Car of the Stars  Makes a Luxurious Comeback

abstract: Cadillac’s flagship sedan is positioned against the best that Audi, BMW, Lexus and Mercedes offer. But this car is more affordable.
snippet: Cadillac’s flagship sedan is positioned against the best that Audi, BMW, Lexus and Mercedes offer. But this car is more affordable.
lead_paragraph: Generally, the one word that describes BMW is “handling.” For Mercedes, it’s “prestige,” Lexus gets “reliability” and for Audi, “design.”
